df <- read.csv("stage1_bogota3_edge.csv")
df
# add the rownames as a proper column
rownames(df) <- NULL
df
head(df)
# Load required packages
library(magrittr)
library(dplyr)
library(ggpubr)
# Cmpute MDS
mds <- df %>%
  dist() %>%          
  cmdscale() %>%
  as_tibble()
Warning in dist(.) : NAs introduced by coercion
colnames(mds) <- c("Dim.1", "Dim.2")
# Plot MDS
ggscatter(mds, x = "Dim.1", y = "Dim.2", 
          label = rownames(df),
          title = "Stage 1 Full Transparency", 
          size = 1,
          repel = TRUE)


# K-means clustering
clust <- kmeans(mds, 3)$cluster %>%
  as.factor()
mds <- mds %>%
  mutate(groups = clust)
# Plot and color by groups
ggscatter(mds, x = "Dim.1", y = "Dim.2", 
          label = rownames(df),
          color = "groups",
          palette = "jco",
          title = "Stage 1 Full Transparency", 
          size = 1, 
          ellipse = TRUE,
          ellipse.type = "convex",
          repel = TRUE)
